messages.text: Are you feeling any better?
What do you think?
:( I’m sorry. i shouldn’t have asked.
I’m sorry…that was mean. You didn’t deserve that.
It’s okay.
I know it’s tough right now.
Right...you guys were pretty close too.
I’m an asshole.
Yeah
It’s fine.
How are you holding up?
I’m not sure.
It’s the first time I’ve lost someone I care about.
Not to spoil anything, but it doesn’t get any easier.
Is that supposed to be comforting?
No. It’s supposed to be messed up.
just like everything else in this broken county.
The system is trying.
I read that they put a whole team together to investigate the house.
Yeah, that’s what you might have read.
But my dad’s been killing himself over all this leg work.
It’s like he’s the only one who even cares.
You care. I care!
Then help me find the bastard that did this and make him pay for it.
I’ll shoot him myself.
What? But the papers are calling it a suicide.
They can’t find anything leading to something else.
I’ve been with my dad through enough cases.
There’s no way in hell this was a suicide.
has he found anything yet?
He thinks he might have but he keeps getting shut down the second he brings it up to his chief.
Really? That’s insane.
Of course it is
No one in this entire station can find anything and once someone does they sweep it under the rug?
I’m sure it’s more complicated than that Amber
It’s not! These officers are selfish and lazy...
and always the first ones to slap a suicide label on any problem that gets too hard!
I mean, this is crazy. I can’t believe he would do that to himself.
He WOULDN’T do that to himself.
I just wish I would have known something. I would see him almost every day.
How did I not notice something?
Amber, seriously.
This isn’t about you. This isn’t about either of us.
What can we even do at this point?
You can keep sitting there not helping.
I rode with my dad to the station to get some answers.
They won’t listen to one of their own.
You think they’re gonna listen to a high schooler?
Wow Luke it’s almost like you’re not on my side or something
I’m trying to cope with my friend’s death just as much as you are.
Sorry if a side effect of that is being a little realistic.
Okay I get you.
It’s late. What do you even plan on doing there?
Can you talk to someone yourself?
My dad and chief are talking.
I’ve been listening outside the door as best as I can.
And if you get nothing?
Then I’ll go to the house myself and look!
That could be dangerous for you!
Save the speech. I know how to use a gun.
And you think a gun is gonna save you? What if something collapses or falls?
I said save the speech.
:/ Well what are they saying in there?
Chief told my dad to lay off the suicide case and find some other work to do.
They just started arguing again.
How long has this been going on.
About half an hour so far.
Wow. Chief really doesn’t want my dad to look much into this one.
Goodness. It’s just a matter of time before it just fades away...
and no one remembers the kid who burned himself and the entire house down!
Maybe you should just of home Amber. There’s nothing for you there to do.
So I’m supposed to sit back and let all this just slide under the rug?
Of course not, but be smart about this.
Me and my dad are being smart.
We’re the only ones even entertaining the idea of a homicide.
I think I just heard my dad bring it up again to the chief.
Homicide? When did that come up?
Whoa they are really loud right now.
Yeah? What are they saying?
Amber?
Amber what’s going on?
Oh my god Luke
Luke I don’t know what to do
There were gunshots in the room!
I started running and didn’t think to check who did what.
My dad…I’m scared for him
Holy crap are you okay?
I have no idea what to do and I’m scared out of my mind!
I’ terrified of calling the police and my dad has his car keys with him.
Can you get to the car? Maybe you can break a window?
Is there a spare key inside? Something to defend yourself with?
You need to get out of there Amber.
NOW
There’s no one else here this late! I can’t even ask someone for help.
Amber i know somewhere close you can go
It’s a friend of mine’s place.
He’ll take care of you until we can get something figured out.
He’ll make sure you’re safe.
Are you serious??
Hurry up and tell me! Drop me the pin do something!
Just go two blocks right from the station and take a left.
First house on the corner!
i’ll tell you when I get there.
Please keep responding I really can’t be alone right now.
I’m here
I promise
Is the house a gross green color?
Almost there!
Yeah? That’s the one?
That’s the one. The door should be open. I told him you were coming.
Okay. I’m in.
Luke
A car just pulled in front of the house!
It’s the chief’s car…
Let him in! Maybe he’s trying to help.
Yeah Luke?
Or maybe he’s trying to come finish the job you asshole!
Honestly Amber
Better him than me. I really liked you.
But you aren’t the only one with friends in the force.
I didn’t want to have to do this again. At least not to you.
I told you this would get dangerous.
But at this point you’ve probably already lost too much blood to hold your phone up.
Give the chief my regards.
How about you give them to him yourself? When you see him in hell
What?!
What happened to the chief?!
Let’s just say I hope you can pull a trigger faster than he could.
Asshole.
